Read and understand https://github.com/MTG/freesound-python/blob/master/Readme.md
Get an api token from freesound.org
Install the freesound library on your local machine with the following steps:
Install github
Download the python egg:
git clone https://github.com/MTG/freesound-python.git
Install the python egg:
python3 setup.py install
Run this python script to discover and download the sound samples


